# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Root .gitignore for sports-app.
#
# app/ and app/android/ ship their own (standard Flutter) .gitignore files that
# already cover the Flutter tree: /build/, .dart_tool/, .flutter-plugins-*,
# /.gradle, gradlew, gradle-wrapper.jar, local.properties, *.iml, .idea/.
# This file covers the worker, the schema tooling, and repo-root artifacts.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Node dependencies — reinstall with `npm install`. Lockfiles ARE committed.
node_modules/

# Cloudflare Wrangler local dev / build state (no secrets, but machine-local).
.wrangler/

# Raw ESPN crawl corpus (schema/tools/crawl.mjs) — hundreds of MB of raw
# responses. The rolled-up guide (schema/espn-guide/) IS committed.
schema/crawl-data/

# Claude Code per-machine state. The workflows/ directory IS committed
# (onboard-league.js is a documented project tool — see CLAUDE.md).
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/scheduled_tasks.lock

# Working artifacts, not deliverables:
#   .scratch/         — throwaway experiments, probes, generated fixtures, logs
#   .playwright-mcp/  — Playwright MCP console/page captures
#   .research-digest.md — raw ESPN reverse-engineering notes (distilled, and
#                         kept authoritative, in schema/SCHEMA.md + canonical.ts)
.scratch/
.playwright-mcp/
.research-digest.md

# Logs
*.log

# OS / editor cruft
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.idea/
*.iml
*.swp
*~
